                        </p>
                    </statement>
                    <solution>
                        <p>
                            Intuitively, "continuous" means small changes in the input result in small changes in the output.
                            This leads to many useful properties of continuous functions, one of which is explored in this
                            section.
                        </p>
                    </solution>
                    
                
